s and implementing effective sales strategies.", "experiences/2/jobEndedOn": "6-2024", "experiences/2/jobStartedOn": "3-2024", "experiences/2/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/2/title": "Sales Executive", "experiences/3/companyName": "Bunta Construction 2560 Company", "experiences/3/jobDescription": "Monitored daily progress on-site to maintain a clear understanding of challenges faced by the team members or any required adjustments in plans or schedules.\n\n•\n\nCommunicated daily with vendors to keep project fully operational.\n\n•\n\nMonitored subcontractor operations and applied effective time, resource, and money management strategies to delivery under-budget project completion.\n\n•\n\nImplemented safety protocols for reduced workplace injuries, conducting regular site inspections and safety meetings.\n\n•\n\nVerified completed projects met approved time, quality, and cost estimates.\n\n•\n\nImproved project efficiency by streamlining communication between architects, engineers, and subcontractors.\n\n•\n\nNegotiated contracts with suppliers and subcontractors to confirm fair pricing and quality service.", "experiences/3/jobEndedOn": "11-2023", "experiences/3/jobStartedOn": "12-2019", "experiences/3/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/3/title": "General Manager", "experiences/4/companyName": "Tripaneer.com", "experiences/4/jobDescription": "Ensuring global customers booking martial arts, yoga and meditation retreats receive exceptional service and support.\n\n•\n\nHandled customer complaints professionally, resulting in satisfactory outcomes and positive feedback.\n\n•\n\nMaintained a high level of product knowledge, providing accurate information to customers.", "experiences/4/jobEndedOn": "1-2020", "experiences/4/jobStartedOn": "1-2018", "experiences/4/jobStillWorking": "false", "experiences/4/title": "Customer Service Specialist", "experiences/5/companyName": "Telstra @Accenture", "experiences/5/jobDescription": "Facilitating the timely and accura